# Client component structure

## Feature-first
- UI lives under `client/src/features/<feature>/components/<Name>/` with `index.tsx` + `<Name>.styles.ts`.
- Route screens under `client/src/features/<feature>/pages/` (e.g. `LoginPage.tsx`).
- Feature-specific helpers: `client/src/features/<feature>/lib/`.

## Shared
- Reusable primitives: `client/src/shared/components/<Name>/`.
- Cross-cutting helpers: `client/src/shared/lib/`.

## Stories
- Storybook is **planned**, not installed. Do not add Storybook in passing; if you add it, do so deliberately and align with @RULES.md.

## Styling
- Tailwind class strings live in `*.styles.ts`, composed in the component (array + `filter(Boolean).join(" ")` pattern).
